{"tid":322931,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"下巴一直生閉口粉刺，點整走?","createTime":"2017-07-15T08:25:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T03:04:36.000Z","uid":111398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fd39c3487f3801cc8d80753b1352d8486a4cfb31","tid":322931,"uid":111398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T08:25:15.000Z","msg":"左邊面下巴有唔少閉口粉刺<br />\n近幾個月先出現，擠又擠唔到<br />\n擠擠下發炎變暗瘡，擠埋粒油滋粒出黎後，又生返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經用左半個月skinoren，早晚全面搽，覺得除左對暗瘡消炎有用之外，對閉口完全冇作用<br />\n想問下有冇巴絲試過啲咩方法搞掂閉口?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b04d97e987d337a6cdc1b55905c25c5cb5c467","tid":322931,"uid":85584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:35:43.000Z","msg":"留名同問"},{"pid":"a8588353e42a807297510abfcd6be06f1a581df0","tid":322931,"uid":2151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:45:32.000Z","msg":"換枕頭袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3395c28db7f28c48715b277d3de79e72fbe13c","tid":322931,"uid":36025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:58:51.000Z","msg":"由細到大都有，所以一路無搞<br />\n近日用the ordinary acid 10% 個支，平左好多"},{"pid":"ca8e0b61be302bc21fd5fd0fd6edccbc6a0d4158","tid":322931,"uid":52539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T18:55:19.000Z","msg":"冇嫁 只可以用酸長時間鬥 半個月太少 起馬都2個月~6個月<br />\n用針挑果D係冇可能搞得掂 實有疤 同只會清到皮毛"},{"pid":"3014001ff44a658bf1c0b064c8b2b0de3b4f6506","tid":322931,"uid":61206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T19:07:37.000Z","msg":"同苦杏仁酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n羅摩有講過"},{"pid":"0f3d396949d5e9f56a65f2e080b521292af5cd97","tid":322931,"uid":43460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T03:04:36.000Z","msg":"用杏仁酸/乳酸（lactic acid)"}]}